Netflix has revealed its most popular shows in South Africa for 2017. It looked at the most popular binge-watched shows, and the shows users “savoured” during the year. The findings showed that 15 October 2017 (a Sunday) was the most popular streaming day of 2017, and also revealed that one Netflix member watched Radio Rebel 191 times in 2017. The tops shows on the platform in South Africa are listed below. Netflix’s data also revealed shows that were popular, but which South Africans watched for less than two hours per day on average.